{
  "stem": "10588.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I realized the power of words, how words can heal and, and kill, how it is.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I started-- everything was the reverse.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It, it was, it was amazing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And all the things that I'd been taught all my life and everything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then, this same Mengele [INAUDIBLE] was such a sadist.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He would take, make, you know, select people and would make operations with people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And some men were castrated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I personally know somebody who lives in Israel who will never, never had a family because he was castrated.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Some didn't survive experiments without, without, without anesthesia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But this I was told by people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If I would have seen, then I would have been one of them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Same like with the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If I would have seen the inside of gas chambers, I wouldn't be here to tell you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But how do I know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because what I found out later.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't know at the time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You see what the Nazis did, is that they selected, they selected people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was called the Sonderkommando, men who work there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they, after three months, they know that they should not, if they survive, they shouldn't survive.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They shouldn't tell what's happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They wanted to destroy, not to have witness.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They would gas them, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And when people would come, including my family, they would send them straight to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But in order that they should not rebel, that they should not, they should go, they told them that they're going to take a bath.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Now, some people came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They didn't have a bath for a long time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So they were glad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they gave them a piece of soap and a towel, and on the door-- because they-- some [INAUDIBLE] will survive.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
